Title: Orders are Orders
Description:
Hmm, maybe wikket not so bad after all!

Other baldskins not nice to hozen.

Hozen take this from bad wikkets!

All wikket loot goes to Kah Kah - Chief's orders!

Here, wikket. You take it. Kah Kah will want to meet new hozen friend.

His camp south at Grookin Hill.
ObjectivesText: Bring the Alliance Orders to Chief Kah Kah at Grookin.
